---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, LEGAL } from '../consts';
---
<LegalLayout title="Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information" description="Your CCPA/CPRA opt-out choices at MoveWell Reviews.">
  <p class="lead">
    Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), as amended by the California Privacy Rights Act
    (CPRA), California residents can opt out of the "sale" or "sharing" of their personal information.
    Similar rights exist under several other U.S. state privacy laws.
  </p>

  <h2>Our position</h2>
  <p>
    {LEGAL.entity} <strong>does not sell your personal information for money.</strong>
    {LEGAL.sharesDataForAds ? (
      <span>
        We do use advertising or analytics partners that may "share" personal information (such as
        cookie or device identifiers) for cross-context behavioral advertising. You can opt out using
        the options below.
      </span>
    ) : (
      <span>
        We do not currently "share" personal information for cross-context behavioral advertising. If
        that ever changes, this page will provide a working opt-out mechanism, and we will update our
        <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> accordingly.
      </span>
    )}
  </p>

  <h2>How to opt out</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Global Privacy Control (GPC):</strong> We honor the
      <a href="https://globalprivacycontrol.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Global Privacy Control</a>
      browser signal. If your browser or extension sends GPC, we treat it as a valid opt-out request.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Cookie banner:</strong> Choose "Decline non-essential" in the consent banner to prevent
      non-essential analytics/advertising cookies from loading.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Email request:</strong> Send a request to
      <a href={`mailto:${LEGAL.privacyEmail}`}>{LEGAL.privacyEmail}</a> with the subject "Do Not Sell
      or Share." We will process verified requests within the timeframe required by law.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Other privacy rights</h2>
  <p>
    You may also request to know, access, correct, or delete your personal information. See our
    <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for the full list of rights and how to exercise them.
    We will not discriminate against you for exercising any privacy right.
  </p>

  <h2>Authorized agents</h2>
  <p>
    You may use an authorized agent to submit a request on your behalf. We may ask the agent for proof
    of authorization and may ask you to verify your identity directly.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Privacy requests: <a href={`mailto:${LEGAL.privacyEmail}`}>{LEGAL.privacyEmail}</a> — or write to
    {LEGAL.entity}, {LEGAL.addressLine1}, {LEGAL.addressLine2}.
  </p>
  <p class="notice">Reminder: This site is {SITE.name}. Replace the placeholder business details in <code>src/consts.js</code> before launch.</p>
</LegalLayout>
